Travel Assistance AI Agent
Overview
Planning a trip? Our **Travel Assistance AI Agent** is your ultimate travel companion! Powered by **Power BI, AI, and OpenAI**,
this smart assistant helps you effortlessly plan your journey from start to finish.
Select your **Start Date**, **End Date**, **Country of Origin**, and **Destination**
Get a **customized travel itinerary** with sightseeing recommendations and local guides
Stay updated with **real-time notes** on weather, local conditions, and travel tips
Discover **geographic insights** for better trip preparation
**Trip Planner:** Get a structured travel plan tailored to your schedule
**Local Guide:** Find must-visit attractions, cultural spots, and hidden gems
**Sightseeing Suggestions:** Know the best places to visit, based on your interests
**Geographic Insights:** Stay informed about weather, terrain, and climate conditions
**Real-time Notes:** Get instant updates for smooth travel planning
**Power BI AI** for data-driven recommendations
**OpenAI** for intelligent insights and itinerary generation
**Real-time updates** to keep your travel plans flexible and stress-free
